title: How much will you earn from Google AdSense in 2020? - Quora

response.answer_text: You will earn from adsense for every ad Click or 1000 ad impression. If your website getting a good amount of traffic in a month then you earn a good amount from Google. If you target high CpC keywords then you earn more from adsense. Upvote and follow if you got your answer
The more - contenttrafficyou will have the more you will earn. Focus on Traffic to earn from Adsense, if you dont have traffic YOU CANNOT EARN FROM ADSENSE.
